text: Unlike some other agents who sell auto/home insurance, Joe Cantrell was professional, very knowledgeable and pleasant. His advice provided me with a policy that has better coverage than my previous carrier at a comparable price. Plus he made our conversation enjoyable. Thanks, Joe!
